---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="about" description="Who is Oddava — a few words, not a resume.">
  <div class="about-content">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm someone who likes to build things and think about how they work.
      I spend a lot of time reading, writing, and tinkering with code — not because
      I'm trying to ship a product, but because the process itself is interesting.
    </p>

    <p>
      This site exists because I wanted a place on the internet that felt like mine.
      Somewhere quiet, without feeds or notifications or engagement metrics.
      A place to put writing that might be useful to someone, or might just be useful to me later.
    </p>

    <p>
      I care about clear thinking, good tools, and making things that last.
      If you're reading this, you probably care about similar things.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can find me on <a href="https://github.com/oddava" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>,
      or reach me at <a href="mailto:hello@oddava.me">hello@oddava.me</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
